snippet.title: Endwar Online: Open Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official launch trailer for EndWar Online, from Ubisoft Shanghai, now in Open Beta! Available worldwide from today. 

In 2030, years of war have left the world in ruins. Rise up from the ashes to complete one final mission, lead your faction to win the war once and for all. 

Play free now: http://bit.ly/1Q0d6Jr

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/endwaronline

Twitter: https://twitter.com/EndWarOnline
